title: We DESTROY Ben Shapiro With FACTS & LOGIC - Leftovers #4
description: On this episode of Leftovers we're in Ben's walls- and he isn't happy about it. Also Ethan and Hasan continue their back and forth over what a socialist future might look like, and take a look at FlagTok- and examine the Civil War the hogs seem to be itching for.
